radicts the common theory of independent action of individual\nbacteria in establishing infections. We discuss the implications of these\nresults.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 15 Sep 2016 20:48:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-06-28"}
