 real functions of\ntwo variables which possess $n$-th partial derivatives of bounded bi-variation,\nLipschitzian and absolutely continuous are established and investigated.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 16 Sep 2016 13:17:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 10 Oct 2019 11:53:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-11"}
